{"tid":196967,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長毛獲批一次性回鄉證 周五北上考察再穿六四Tee闖關？","createTime":"2017-04-11T15:30:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-14T03:13:31.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6199a4c07f29bd4dc6526839418f39fcfcfe274c","tid":196967,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-11T15:30:29.000Z","msg":"立法會發展事務委員會將於本周五到廣東考察東江水供水系統，已報名參加考察團的社民連梁國雄日前到旺角中旅社申請一次性回鄉證，今日獲批出證件。過去曾因穿六四tee而被內地拒入境，被問到今次會否擔心不能入境，他僅說：「問大陸。」<br />\n<br />\n他又指過去曾著六四tee亦能過關，重申2005年及2007年均以立法會議員身份到內地。至於會否有考察以外的行動或約見內地人士，他則說暫未知能否入境，又怎會事先約人。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56550728&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170411\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56550728%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170411&d=6Nb1RK4hIZDTz%2Fb962Zoj8mDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=5d107c8a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56550728%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170411&h=d0a21f75\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56550728&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170411</a>"},{"pid":"f99aeecdae274a40b8b9f423b02cc7a271d30d0b","tid":196967,"uid":55990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T03:13:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}